Package org.alljoyn.ns.commons

The package includes generic classes that are used by other packages of the Notification service

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenericLogger
    Implement this interface to provide logging functionality for the Notification service
    NativePlatform
    Implement this interface to provide platform dependent functionality for the Notification service
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NativePlatformAbstrImpl
    The abstract parent class for all the classes implementing platform dependent logic
    NativePlatformFactory
    The factory class for the classes extending NativePlatformAbstrImpl
    According to the platform that the service is running on, the appropriate platform dependent class is instantiated and returned
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NativePlatformFactoryException
    The exception is thrown if there was a failure in loading and instantiating the class implementing platform dependent logic
